headline: TRU Simulation’s Full Flight Simulator for the Cessna Citation Ascend Achieves FAA Qualification, Expanding Advanced Training for Midsize Jet Pilots
summary: TAMPA, Fla., February 16, 2026--TRU Simulation + Training Inc. announced its Full Flight Simulator for the Cessna Citation Ascend has achieved FAA Level D qualification.
